g/kg, which is associated with compromised immunity. These are the first published records of contaminant concentrations from bats in China. For future studies, we recommend P. abramus as a regional bioindicator, longer term assessments of pre- and postexposure effects, and simultaneous assessment of blood and fur Hg concentrations.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Heiker, Laura M.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Adams, Rick A.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Ramos, Claire V.", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/8b3491a8e8fde35e4459374ebf0e751a", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/2c27e78215a8a9a6fd35f7d647f50b0c1a66c5022e46895cec14cc6914d447f6", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/XZU7DFTZ", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/XZU7DFTZ", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/69b406ec47c606b5869c7da332fdb0c1!/b118340-120804", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "4", "pages": "585-593", "title": "Archives of Environmental Contamination and Toxicology", "volume": "75"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/8b3491a8e8fde35e4459374ebf0e751a"}, {"identifier": "urn:lsid:zotero.org:groups:5435545:items:XZU7DFTZ"}, {"i